</span> is transmit frequency, <span class="mwe-math-element" typeof="mw:Extension/math" about="#mwt342" data-mw='{"name":"math","attrs":{},"body":{"extsrc":"V_R"}}' id="mwAWA"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttext="{\displaystyle V_{R}}">
  <semantics>
    <mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
      <mstyle displaystyle="true" scriptlevel="0">
