          <mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
            <mi>R</mi>
          </mrow>
        </msub>
      </mstyle>
    </mrow>
    <annotation encoding="application/x-tex">{\displaystyle V_{R}}</annotation>
  </semantics>
</math></span><img src="https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/render/svg/d3ba1cd5708f2c5230fb763aa5a5ac5f3efbc229" class="mwe-math-fallback-image-inline" aria-hidden="true" style="vertical-align: -0.671ex; width:2.835ex; height:2.509ex;" alt="V_{R}"/></span><span about="#mwt342">
</span> is radial velocity, and <span class="mwe-math-element" typeof="mw:Extension/math" about="#mwt344" data-mw='{"name":"math","attrs":{},"body":{"extsrc":"C"}}' id="mwAWE"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttext="{\displaystyle C}">
  <semantics>
    <mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
      <mstyle displaystyle="true" scriptlevel="0">
        <mi>C</mi>
      </mstyle>
    </mrow>
    <annotation encoding="application/x-tex">{\displaystyle C}</annotation>
  </semantics>
</math></span><img src="https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/render/svg/4fc55753007cd3c18576f7933f6f089196732029" class="mwe-math-fallback-image-inline" aria-hidden="true" style="vertical-align: -0.338ex; width:1.766ex; height:2.176ex;" alt="C"/></span><span about="#mwt344">
</span> is the speed of light:<sup about="#mwt369" class="mw-ref" id="cite_ref-35" rel="dc:references" typeof="mw:Extension/ref" data-mw='{"name":"ref","attrs":{},"body":{"id":"mw-reference-text-cite_note-35"}}'><a href="./Radar#cite_note-35" style="counter-reset: mw-Ref 35;"><span class="mw-reflink-text">[35]</span></a></sup></p>

<dl id="mwAWI"><dd id="mwAWM"><span class="mwe-math-element" typeof="mw:Extension/math" about="#mwt347" data-mw='{"name":"math","attrs":{},"body":{"extsrc":"F_D =  2 \\times F_T \\times \\left (\\frac {V_R}{C} \\right)"}}' id="mwAWQ"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttext="{\displaystyle F_{D}=2\times F_{T}\times \left({\frac {V_{R}}{C}}\right)}">
